{"word":"H3726 - כְּפַר הָעַמֹּונִי - Kᵉphar hâ-ʻAmmôwnîy - kef-ar' haw-am-monee' - Chefarhaamonai","slug":"H3726","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כְּפַר הָעַמֹּונִי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Kᵉphar hâ-ʻAmmôwnîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kef-ar' haw-am-monee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Chefarhaamonai"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05E4;&#x05E8; &#x05D4;&#x05E2;&#x05DE;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05E0;&#x05D9; - k<sup>e</sup>phar ha&#x0302;&#x201B;ammo&#x0302;n&#x0131;&#x0302;y</b> - <i>kef-ar' haw-am-mo-nee'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H3723\">H3723</a> and <a href=\"#/H5984\">H5984</a>, with the article interposed; <i>village of the Ammonite</i>; <i>Kefarha Ammoni</i>, a place in Palestine: - Chefar-haamonai."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3715\">H3715</a>, <a href=\"#/H3716\">H3716</a>, <a href=\"#/H3723\">H3723</a>, <a href=\"#/H3724\">H3724</a>"}]}